cu.explanation_en: Setting global_log_level to a nonexistent value will cause logging configuration errors, potentially leading to silent failures or excessive logging that impacts performance.

du.explanation_en: Setting global_log_level to a nonexistent value will cause logging configuration errors, potentially leading to silent failures or excessive logging that impacts performance.
du.explanation_zh: 將 global_log_level 設定為不存在的值將導致日誌配置錯誤，可能導致靜默失敗或過度日誌記錄影響性能。
